# AISU Designation Management — Complete System

## Answers to Your Questions

### Is Dashboard and Admin the same?
**Yes.** `admin.html` is the single admin dashboard/portal. It contains all panels (Primary Members, Role Management, Designations, Approvals, History, etc.) accessed via the sidebar.

### Correct Flow Implemented

```
Primary Membership Form → Pending → Approved (Primary Member only, ID generated)
                                         ↓
                     Designations Panel → Appoint (assign designation)
                                         ↓
                     Privileges granted based on designation
                                         ↓
                     Our Team page auto-updated
```

---

## What Changed

### 1. Member Approval Flow (Fixed)
- **Before:** Approval prompted for level + designation → wrong
- **Now:** Approval → auto-assigns "Primary Member" at "member" level only
- Member ID is generated when form is submitted (it was already correct)
- Designation is assigned LATER via the **Designations** panel (Appoint action)

### 2. All 10 Administrative Actions Now Available

| Action | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| **Promote** | `POST /rbac/promote/{id}` | Elevate member to higher designation |
| **Demote** | `POST /rbac/demote/{id}` | Lower member's designation |
| **Transfer** | `POST /rbac/transfer/{id}` | Move to different state/district |
| **Add Additional Charge** | `POST /rbac/additional-role/{id}` | Give extra designation (max 3) |
| **Remove Additional Charge** | `POST /rbac/remove-additional-role/{id}` | Strip an additional designation |
| **Suspend** | `POST /rbac/suspend/{id}` | Suspend for N days (days required) |
| **Dismiss** | `POST /rbac/dismiss/{id}` | Permanently remove from organization |
| **Approve Resignation** | `POST /rbac/approve-resignation/{id}` | Accept member's resignation |
| **Assign Designation** | `POST /rbac/assign-designation/{id}` | First appointment (auto) or additional (needs approval) |
| **Approve/Reject Multi-Designation** | `POST /rbac/approve-designation/{id}` | Top-4 approve 2nd/3rd designations |

### 3. Suspension Details
- Admin must specify **number of days** when suspending
- `suspended_until` date calculated automatically
- Member's user account status → `suspended`
- Member hidden from Our Team page during suspension

### 4. Our Team Auto-Update
The `team.html` page auto-excludes members with status:
- `resigned`, `terminated`, `expired`, `suspended`, `dismissed`

### 5. History/Audit Trail
**All actions** are logged in `promotion_history` and visible under the **Promotion History** panel. Top-4 national officers can filter by any of these action types:
- Membership Approved, Appointed, Promoted, Demoted, Transferred
- Additional Charge, Charge Removed, Suspended, Dismissed, Resignation

### 6. Student Membership & User Roles
**Not touched** — Student membership and regular user flows remain unchanged.

### 7. No Unnecessary Files
All files in the backend are required. No files were removed.

